data.description: Situated conveniently near McCreless Shopping Center, this 2-bedroom, 1 full-bathroom gem is a perfect haven for those valuing proximity to amenities and downtown accessibility. A detached garage, ripe for transformation-envision a workshop, art studio, or a revamped separate living space. The reasonably sized backyard offers space for personal touches, whether you want a garden patch or a cozy outdoor sitting area. Protect your car from the weather under the covered parking spot. Seize the chance to own a home with great potential.
